%^BOLD%^BLACK%^ULINE%^Ghoul Bloodline%^RESET%^

Your connection to the hungering undead shapes your magic.

%^BLACK%^BOLD%^Bloodline Arcana:%^RESET%^
Dealing negative energy damage with spells heals you slightly.

%^BLACK%^BOLD%^Ghoulish Aspect (L31):%^RESET%^
You take on the manner and appearance of a ghoul, gaining increased resistance to paralysis (on cooldown).

%^BOLD%^BLACK%^Bonus Bloodline Skill%^RESET%^: stealth

%^BOLD%^BLACK%^Bonus Spells%^RESET%^: chill touch, ray of enfeeblement, vampiric touch, boneshatter, teleport, circle of death, finger of death, horrid wilting
